{"tid":1409632,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"下次有人影相，唔好再瘋狂怒屌，試下多點關懷多點愛","createTime":"2019-08-04T23:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T23:47:21.000Z","uid":271762,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3822bd0fa91d44b316ef504db3a182e5bb8d173f","tid":1409632,"uid":271762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:08:46.000Z","msg":"呢個星期好明顯feel到大家越來越冇耐性，一見到有人影大家就起晒鋼<br />\n首先想幫大家認清楚點先要阻人影相<br />\n追住手足黎影，影大頭<br />\n影緊手足做正經野<br />\n張相涉及手足私隱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想比少少提議<br />\n首先，比人影街境其實好閒，反正我地都包到實一實，不如先試下好聲好氣，呼籲返唔好影正面，唔好影敏感野<br />\n<br />\n好多上年紀既人係咁八卦咖啦，<span style=\"color: red;\">尤其是我地呢個月以黎散晒落社區玩</span>，呢個好有可能係佢哋電視以外，親身接觸我地既時候。我地都要念及佢哋唔識規舉，其實肯花少少耐心，佢哋都係易話為既，我地落到區就當做show親民下啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地唔好一見到人地舉cam就去圍佢，我地每個人見到有人就近影相，都埋去關注一下先，可以禮貌文明地解決就最好，講極唔明先埋去幫口，起口角先至圍，咁樣。<br />\n<br />\n我地要分清楚自己係人，唔係狗，我哋識禮貌，講道理，唔會見人就插。但係同時我地都唔會比人蝦都上心口都唔還拖。"},{"pid":"26218eb097b4ef025e85eb8c05b3e6676dbc776c","tid":1409632,"uid":271762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:10:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95dc41a29f6e754e15044964a8585e592fee410e","tid":1409632,"uid":55384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:12:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc847d7d1602b65ea800dfc02260ebe5bf061b26","tid":1409632,"uid":271762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:30:41.000Z","msg":"見到廢老話阻撚住晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不要</span>隻揪啊屌你老母<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">試著</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e10560b90d2c27f47488dba45a538bbb82d3829","tid":1409632,"uid":271762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285bdf5f3f2faea3707a42902c7c6eb44e6016d1","tid":1409632,"uid":271762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1391e01bf549d3549679875070a23ef4dbc3e01","tid":1409632,"uid":280746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:47:21.000Z","msg":"我都好八卦，都會影示威相<br />\n但唔會影住人嘅大頭相追住你影囉<br />\n唔好美化潛在臥底"}]}